solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int numDecodings(String s) {--newline--        int n = s.length();--newline--        if (n == 0) return 0;--newline--        --newline--        int[] memo = new int[n+1];--newline--        memo[n]  = 1;--newline--        memo[n-1] = s.charAt(n-1) != '0' ? 1 : 0;--newline--        --newline--        for (int i = n - 2; i >= 0; i--)--newline--            if (s.charAt(i) == '0') continue;--newline--            else memo[i] = (Integer.parseInt(s.substring(i,i+2))<=26) ? memo[i+1]+memo[i+2] : memo[i+1];--newline--        --newline--        return memo[0];--newline--    }--newline--}
